on a silver platter.

01:30:01.000 --> 01:30:05.437
- That silver's turned to iron bars, Nicky.
- Don't hate me, Miss Piggy.

01:30:05.520 --> 01:30:08.956
Oh, I don't.
It's just that somehow along the road

01:30:09.040 --> 01:30:11.554
I found out the difference
between wrong and right.

01:30:11.640 --> 01:30:13.835
You're wrong...

01:30:13.920 --> 01:30:16.070
He's right.

01:30:20.280 --> 01:30:24.512
Would you believe it, Statler? They're
heroes. Now they're gonna be obnoxious.

01:30:24.600 --> 01:30:26.716
So what else is new?

01:30:27.640 --> 01:30:32.156
- Well, I say all's well that ends well.
- It doesn't matter to me as long as it ends.

01:30:39.680 --> 01:30:42.194
It was nice of the <i>Chronicle</i>
